<HL>
   Credit Ratings:
   Six Railroads' Rating
   On Trust Certificates
   Downgraded by S&amp;P
</HL>
<DATE>
10/29/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A24
</SO>
<CO>
   CNW IC SFX X.AFE
</CO>
